        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> We do not have a verify job to pick these files. Do we need to add them? Do any of our templates apply?\n\nno, we have a discussion on that since some weeks\nin all the integration related repositories, there are very few verification jobs\nhttps://wiki.onap.org/display/DW/Verification+jobs+on+Integration+repositories\nhere for instance there is even no INFO.yaml, I assumed it was inheriting from testsuite but it is not the case, so rights are not propagated\nI should \n- add a info-verify job\n- add info\n- add additional verification jobs (python/java/bash/robot/whatever/..)\n\nwe decided today to start with integration repo, we want also to be verified :)",
